// TCO Analysis Template (3-year horizon)
// Build Option:
//   Year 1: 6 engineers x $300K = $1.8M + infrastructure $200K = $2.0M
//   Year 2: 3 engineers x $300K = $0.9M + infrastructure $400K = $1.3M
//   Year 3: 3 engineers x $300K = $0.9M + infrastructure $800K = $1.7M
//   Total: $5.0M
//
// Buy Option:
//   Year 1: License $500K + integration 2 engineers x $300K = $1.1M
//   Year 2: License $600K + vendor management 0.5 engineer = $0.75M
//   Year 3: License $720K + vendor management 0.5 engineer = $0.87M
//   Total: $2.72M
//
// But if the capability is core, the build option gives control, customization,
// and competitive advantage that may be worth the extra $2.28M
